_:N945808d9615a49c1b8cb0d40e980bbdc <http://schema.org/description> "<p>The Rt Hon Baroness Smith of Malvern was appointed Minister of State (Minister for Skills) in the Department for Education on 6 July 2024. This role also became part of the Department for Work and Pensions on 6 September 2025.</p>\n\n<p>Since 4 March 2025, the Rt Hon Baroness Smith of Malvern has also served as Minister of State (Minister for Women and Equalities).</p>\n\n<p>She previously served  as a Government Spokesperson for Equalities between 8 October 2024 and 4 March 2025.</p>\n" <https://forgetmenot.local/extractor/jsonld> .
