<https://www.gov.uk/government/people/jacqui-smith> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "The Rt Hon Baroness Smith of Malvern was appointed Minister of State (Minister for Skills) in the Department for Education on 6 July 2024. This role also became part of the Department for Work and Pensions on 6 September 2025. Since 4 March 2025, the Rt Hon Baroness Smith of Malvern has also served as Minister of State (Minister for Women and Equalities). She previously served as a Government Spokesperson for Equalities between 8 October 2024 and 4 March 2025."@en <https://forgetmenot.local/extractor/rdfa> .
